/script EatFood()

function EatFood()
    -- Don't eat if in combat
    if UnitAffectingCombat("player") then
        return
    end
  
    -- Don't eat if already eating
    if buffed("Food", "player") or buffed("Drink", "player") then
        return
    end
  
    -- Try to use items directly - let the game handle if they exist or not
    UseItemByName("Conjured Mana Orange")
    UseItemByName("Enriched Manna Biscuit")
end



Sort priority by sorting the Food in order:
    UseItemByName("Conjured Mana Orange")
    UseItemByName("Enriched Manna Biscuit")

Uses "Conjured Mana Orange" -> "Enriched Manna Biscuit" -> etc.
